@prefix : <https://www.w3id.org/climoo#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix xml: <http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@base <https://www.w3id.org/climoo#> .

<https://www.w3id.org/climoo> rdf:type owl:Ontology ;
                               owl:versionIRI :V1.0.0 ;
                               owl:imports <http://ClimOO/climoo/import/sumso-imports#2025-06-16> ,
                                           <http://ClimOO/climoo/imports/cco-imports#2025-06-17> ,
                                           <http://ClimOO/climoo/imports/envo-imports#2025-06-25> ,
                                           <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/climoo/imports/chebi_imports#2025-06-19> ,
                                           <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/climoo/imports/pato_imports#2025-06-19> ,
                                           <https://ClimOO/climoo/imports/iao-imports#2025-06-18> ,
                                           <https://www.w3id.org/sco/sco-b#v1.1.0/sco-b> ;
                               <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> "Giorgio A. Ubbiali" ;
                               <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "ClimOO is a domain ontology, modeling (micro-)plastic pollution, climate change and their interrelation, with a primary focus on local South Tyrolean (Italy) agricultural production."@en ;
                               <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> "https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/" ;
                               <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "ClimOO Ontology"@en ;
                               rdfs:comment """Two new releases of CCO, CCO 1.7 and CCO 2.0, have been made available in November 2024. CCO 2.0 provides a new IRI schema. SCO, ClimOO upper-level ontology, imports from a former release. CCO 1.5. Similarly, SuMSO, another ontology extending SCO from which ClimOO reuses several backbone classes as backbone, imports from CCO 1.6. Aiming to conform with established sustainability ontologies, ClimOO currently reuses CCO imports from SCO and SuMSO. As soon as updates will been made available for those resources, ClimOO will align accordingly. 
ClimOO also reuse some classes from CCO that are not imported by SCO and SuMSO. Those imports have been fletched from CCO 2.0 and imports’ harmonization has been performed manually to ensure ontology structure and IRIs accuracy and correspondence as needed.  

https://github.com/CommonCoreOntology/CommonCoreOntologies/releases
https://github.com/gioUbbiali/Sustainability-Core-Ontology 
https://github.com/gioUbbiali/Sustainable-Meat-Systems-Ontology"""@en ;
                               owl:versionInfo "2025-06-07"@en ,
                                               "V1.0.0." ;
                               <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#note> """Repository: https://github.com/ClimOO/ClimOO-Ontology
Documentation webpage: https://www.w3id.org/climoo/docs"""@en ,
                                                                          "The most recent version of this file is available on GitHub at the following link: https://www.w3id.org/climoo"@en .

