###  https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000160
<https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000160> rdfs:subClassOf <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_01000665> .

[ rdf:type owl:Axiom ;
   owl:annotatedSource <https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000160> ;
   owl:annotatedProperty rdfs:subClassOf ;
   owl:annotatedTarget <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_01000665> ;
   rdfs:comment """ClimOO developer comment:
This class presents a narrower focus than the EnvO class from which it has been adapted. Thus, we considered this class as a subclass of the original EnvO class."""@en
 ] .


###  https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00000120
<https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00000120> rdfs:subClassOf [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                     owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000235> ;
                                                                     owl:someValuesFrom <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000003>
                                                                   ] ;
                                                   rdfs:comment """ClimOO developer comment:
